{"word":"G4916 - συνθάπτω - syntháptō - soon-thap'-to - Bury with","slug":"G4916","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συνθάπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>syntháptō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>soon-thap'-to"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bury with"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C5;&#x03BD;&#x03B8;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C0;&#x03C4;&#x03C9; - sunthapto&#x0304;</b> - <i>soon-thap'-to</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G2290\">G2290</a>; to <i>inter</i> in company <i>with</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>assimilate</i> spiritually (to Christ by a sepulture as to sin): - bury with."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4776\">G4776</a>, <a href=\"#/G4789\">G4789</a>, <a href=\"#/G4800\">G4800</a>, <a href=\"#/G4806\">G4806</a>, <a href=\"#/G4821\">G4821</a>, <a href=\"#/G4832\">G4832</a>, <a href=\"#/G4833\">G4833</a>, <a href=\"#/G4841\">G4841</a>, <a href=\"#/G4854\">G4854</a>, <a href=\"#/G4855\">G4855</a>, <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a>, <a href=\"#/G4880\">G4880</a>, <a href=\"#/G4888\">G4888</a>, <a href=\"#/G4891\">G4891</a>, <a href=\"#/G4957\">G4957</a>"}]}